	<h1 class="title">四月泡面新番《猫猫日本史》，把织田信长变成猫</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/117425/small/117425.?1433669313" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王珊珊 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-13 07:09:51 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/25351/medium/25351.jpg?1460452227" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


